Uses of Package
owlSpeak

  • Packages that use owlSpeak 
    Package Description
    owlSpeak
    This package contains all classes needed to access and modify the Spoken Dialogue Ontologies and provides a ready-to-use factory class.
    owlSpeak.engine
    This package provides all classes the controller needs to generate the next dialogue steps.
    owlSpeak.engine.his
    This package provides all classes for extending the dialogue control to the hidden information state approach.
    owlSpeak.engine.his.interfaces  
    owlSpeak.engine.his.sysAction  
    owlSpeak.engine.policy  
    owlSpeak.engine.systemState  
    owlSpeak.imports  
    owlSpeak.lgus  
    owlSpeak.quality  
    owlSpeak.servlet
    This package provides the classes that define the various views OwlSpeak supports.
    owlSpeak.servlet.grammar
